.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, rowing, soccer, may-polo, cricket
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, skateboard, boat, snowmobile, bike
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, february, september, august, may
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: fantasy, drama, romance, satire, mystery
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, balloon-flower, aconite, begonia, daffodil
1. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's sport is soccer
2. the person driving the swedish is the person who growsaconite
3. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's birthday is in august
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is may-polo
5. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's birthday is in february
6. the person watching romance movies is the person who growsballoon-flower
7. the person who's sport is cricket is the person watching drama movies
8. the person who's birthday is in september is in the middle
9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left
10. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower
11. the person who growsdaffodils is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies
12. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's birthday is in april
13. the person driving the boat is the person watching satire movies
14. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing
15. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may

.:: Answer ::.
